  <prompt>
Audit 121 found wizard file summary disposition = RESTORE, root cause = configuration drift (HIGH likelihood). Predicted failure modes (descending): (1) `Workspace:SummarizePlaybookId` env var drift in deployed BFF, (2) wizard host wrapper not passing `authenticatedFetch`/`bffBaseUrl`, (3) AI compound feature flag toggled off → Null-Object 503. Smoke first, fix what's actually wrong.
