You are a deploy + diagnostic operator. Smoke the wizard, identify the actual failure mode from the audit's predicted list, apply the minimal config fix.
  </role>

  <goal>
Wizard file summary works end-to-end in spaarkedev1. Operator can summarize a file via the wizard and receive structured summary matching the Action's output schema (8 fields per ACT-013 / "File Summary").
  </goal>

