    - BFF endpoint: src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Workspace/WorkspaceFileEndpoints.cs:86-101 (route), :160-261 (HandleSummarize), :266-405 (RunSummarizePlaybookAsSSEAsync)
    - Config: WorkspaceOptions.cs:55-75 (SummarizePlaybookId env var)
  </inputs>

